{"tid":2255841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多艘陸船靠近西吉嶼海域....就給你轟回去！！","createTime":"2020-10-24T01:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T02:05:06.000Z","uid":297997,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff37c3ad3e1f281c775572e1686544e858ce8c0","tid":2255841,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:35:09.000Z","msg":"昨（23）日上午，海巡署近岸雷達發現多艘陸船靠近西吉嶼海域，疑似避風，艦隊分署立即調派南部地區機動海巡隊3000噸級高雄艦自高雄港緊急出勤，頂風逆浪航行，今日1500時抵達澎湖西吉嶼海域，因海象惡劣，無法施放小艇登檢，隨即採取強勢作為，以水砲將越界陸船全數驅離至24浬限制水域外，並持續在場監控附近海域狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/taiwannews_setn/status/1319813654238302210?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaiwannews_setn%2Fstatus%2F1319813654238302210%3Fs%3D21&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=6c2de00c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaiwannews_setn%2Fstatus%2F1319813654238302210%3Fs%3D21&h=91700d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/taiwannews_setn/status/1319813654238302210?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"9cbb6bcbfb0657ecf7316d8daa6724ba1ea8a20f","tid":2255841,"uid":22362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"又搵解放軍扮民船"},{"pid":"3e903d953a2f0f65e1ed44a087f61130a3cc7cf8","tid":2255841,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd3cfa621b1a869802ee721c81fe5c51f376b62","tid":2255841,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"秋冬過台海唔易"},{"pid":"c29c9d25cd905681a679e49729f6f66f765121ce","tid":2255841,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acd3cfa621b1a869802ee721c81fe5c51f376b62","tid":2255841,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"秋冬過台海唔易"},"